<p>It’s time for the latest game announcements for April 3, 2025.</p>



<p>Every week new games are announced or major updates come for previously announced titles. Sometimes, it happens at such a pace that it’s impossible for the average player to keep up with the latest details. </p>



<p>The last week has been one of those weeks. And no matter how big or small, we want to make sure you know about the latest game reveals, updates, and release date announcements. Oh, and if you notice a lot of Nintendo games, that’s for good reason as the company had not one, but two directs over the last week.</p>



<h6>RELATED: <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-nintendo-direct-everything-announced/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Nintendo Switch 2 Nintendo Direct: Everything Announced</a></h6>



<p>If you are a developer, publisher, or agency that wants to make sure your games are included in the next round up, please <strong>email senior editor Mike Straw at <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#0b466268636a6e674b426578626f6e79264c6a6662656c25686466" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><span data-cfemail="c18ca8a2a9a0a4ad8188afb2a8a5a4b3ec86a0aca8afa6efa2aeac">[email&nbsp;protected]</span></a>.</strong> A new round up goes live each week.</p>



<p>If you missed last week’s announcements, you can <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/latest-game-announcements-march-26-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">see them here</a>. Are there any announcements you’re particularly excited about? Let us know down below, and join the discussion in the official <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/forum/threads/1809/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Insider Gaming Forums</a>.</p>



<hr>



<h2 id="h-latest-video-game-announcements-april-3-2025">Latest Video Game Announcements – April 3, 2025</h2>



<p><strong>Marvel Cosmic Invasion — <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/marvel-cosmic-invasion-announced-for-2025-release/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">FULL STORY</a></strong></p>



<p>Marvel Cosmic Invasion sees you select a team of two heroes to fight your way through enemies in order to stop Annihilus’ attack on the galaxy. The game will also feature four-player drop-in/drop-out multiplayer both online and locally. The game is scheduled to release later this year for PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and PC.</p>



