        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[All Nintendo Switch 2 Launch Titles—Every Switch 2 Exclusive Revealed]]></title>
            <link>https://insider-gaming.com/all-nintendo-switch-2-release-titles/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/all-nintendo-switch-2-launch-titles%E2%80%94every-switch-2-exclusive-revealed.1153992/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://insider-gaming.com/all-nintendo-switch-2-release-titles/<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>Exciting launch titles are a big reason to get a Switch 2 on day one. The Nintendo Switch 2 already has a fair few big-name games ready for the Switch 2 release, and I know you’re also here to see what exclusives the Japanese game company has up its sleeves.</p>



<p>A new console generation hinges on several variables: Its <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-price-officially-confirmed-at-449-99/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">price</a>, the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-features-officially-revealed/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">features</a> and specs, and software. The <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-nintendo-direct-everything-announced/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Nintendo Switch 2 Direct</a> finally revealed much of this and gave people reasons to buy the new console. You want better graphics? The new <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-4k-120fps-hdr/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">4K, HDR, and 120 FPS</a> upgrades will do this. Want to revisit your favorite GameCube games in 2025? Say hello to the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-online-adds-gamecube-games-to-nintendo-switch-2-release/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">GameCube Switch Online</a> integration.</p>



<p>But it’s new games that sell consoles, let’s face it. So let’s see which Nintendo Switch 2 games are currently releasing for launch.</p>



<h2 id="h-every-nintendo-switch-2-launch-game">Every Nintendo Switch 2 Launch Game</h2>



<figure><figcaption>Some smashing games are on the way. Credit to Nintendo</figcaption></figure>



<p>By “launch,” we quite literally mean playable games the second the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-release-date-announced/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Nintendo Switch 2 release date</a> is hit. A handful of titles are scheduled for July and beyond, but they’re not what we’re looking for today.</p>



<p>Here’s every game you can look forward to if you pre-order your <a href="https://www.nintendo.com/us/gaming-systems/switch-2/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch 2</a> to be ready on day one:</p>



<ul>
<li>Arcade Archives 2 RIDGE RACER</li>



<li><a href="https://insider-gaming.com/borderlands-4-switch-2/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Borderlands 4</a></li>



<li>Bravely Default</li>



<li>Civilization 7</li>



<li><a href="https://insider-gaming.com/cyberpunk-2077-ultimate-edition-switch-2/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Cyberpunk 2077: Ultimate Edition</a></li>



<li>Deltarune</li>



<li>Drag x Drive</li>



<li>EA Sports FC</li>



<li>Fast Fusion</li>



<li>Fortnite</li>



<li>Hitman: World of Assassination</li>



<li>Hogwarts Legacy</li>



<li>Human Fall Flat 2</li>



<li>Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess</li>



<li>Madden NFL</li>



<li><a href="https://insider-gaming.com/mario-kart-world-revealed-as-nintendo-switch-2-launch-title/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mario Kart World</a></li>



<li>Nobunaga’s Ambition: Awakening Complete Edition</li>



<li>Puyo Puyo Tetris 2S</li>



<li>Rune Factory: Guardians of Azuma</li>



<li>Street Fighter 6</li>



<li>Split Fiction</li>



<li>Survival Kids</li>



<li>Yakuza 0: Director’s Cut</li>
</ul>



<p>We have an extended list of <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/all-games-announced-during-the-nintendo-switch-2-direct/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">all games announced for the Switch 2</a> as well. The console’s first year should be a meaty one with lots of gaming to be done.</p>



<h2 id="h-all-nintendo-switch-2-exclusive-games">All Nintendo Switch 2 Exclusive Games</h2>



<p>The Nintendo Switch 2 exclusive list is much shorter but expected to grow. It includes some of Nintendo’s most iconic franchises (as expected), and the future looks rosier than a shy-looking Kirby.</p>



<p>There are plenty of other Nintendo games arriving in 2025, from <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/new-metroid-prime-4-beyond-gameplay-revealed-at-nintendo-direct/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Metroid Prime 4</a> to <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/pokemon-legends-z-a-release-platforms-price/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Pokémon Legends Z-A</a>, but these can also be found on the Nintendo Switch 1. </p>



<p>We’re looking at the sole reasons to invest in the Nintendo Switch 2, so check out the exclusive list so far.</p>



<figure><table><thead><tr><th data-align="center">Nintendo Switch 2 Game Name</th><th data-align="center">Release Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-align="center">Donkey Kong Bananza</td><td data-align="center">July 17</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Drag x Drive</td><td data-align="center">Launch Day</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Hyrule Warriors: Age of Imprisonment</td><td data-align="center">2025</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Kirby Air Riders</td><td data-align="center">2025</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Mario Kart World</td><td data-align="center">Launch Day</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Nintendo Switch 2 Welcome Tour</td><td data-align="center">Launch Day</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Survival Kids</td><td data-align="center">Launch Day</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">The Duskbloods</td><td data-align="center">2026</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<hr>



<p>What do you think of the Switch 2 lineup? Do any particular games catch your eye? Let us know which games you’re hoping are announced soon via our <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/forum/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Insider Gaming Forum</a>.</p>



<p>The Switch 2 details don’t stop here. We have information on <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/nintendo-switch-2-pre-orders-are-already-live-in-the-uk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">how to get an early pre-order</a>, <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/how-much-will-nintendo-switch-2-games-cost-physical-digital-game-prices-explained/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">how much the games cost</a>, and <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/what-is-the-nintendo-switch-2-battery-life/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">what the console’s battery life</a> is.</p>
